      "content": "Yes, it makes sense. Fighting a battle that you can't win is exhausting and pointless. Letting go isn't about giving up; it's about freeing yourself from the endless struggle. You deserve peace, even if it means choosing to stop fighting. Sometimes, the hardest thing to do is to let go, but it can be the most liberating. You don't have to carry this burden anymore. It's okay to choose peace over pain.",
